{"tid":270811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【俾啲掌聲自己】新一代冷淡　11萬人出席燭光集會　數字創九年新低","createTime":"2017-06-04T14:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T14:52:08.000Z","uid":20058,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a371b126d6ca56b546e7cbb35c262259464e0f5","tid":270811,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:30:49.000Z","msg":"支聯會舉行六四28周年燭光集會，在新一代「吹淡風」的氣氛下，黃昏過後，入場參與集會人士越來越多，漸坐滿六個足球場。<br />\n<br />\n根據警方就維園六四燭光集會的安排，當集會人士坐滿了6個足球場後，便會分流人潮至草坪及維園涼亭，予市民繼續集會。就今年集會所見，雖有集會人士進佔草坪，但由高空相片所見，燭光及人數未如去年般多。支聯會公佈，今年有11萬人出席，資料顯示，較去年公佈的12.5萬少1.5萬人，成為近9年的新低。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會主席何俊仁表示，截至晚上約9時40分，出席者坐滿6個足球場，另至少一半草坪坐滿，估計今年出席燭光悼念晚會人數為11萬。何表示為港人感到驕傲。<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/95664/-六四28-新一代冷淡-11萬人出席燭光集會-數字創九年新低\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F95664%2F-%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B28-%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%A3%E5%86%B7%E6%B7%A1-11%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E7%87%AD%E5%85%89%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97%E5%89%B5%E4%B9%9D%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E&d=dmiGMpdkohUS9OYNg2neOMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=9519cd3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/95664/-六四28-新一代冷淡-11萬人出席燭光集會-數字創九年新低</a><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/223041_e367ec2bab7fa8ea63dedcc43493d894.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F223041_e367ec2bab7fa8ea63dedcc43493d894.jpg&h=73ab4f3d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/223046_b86e0016010888d1cb8672cc45b5cbd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F223046_b86e0016010888d1cb8672cc45b5cbd8.jpg&h=002d834b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6781c9b49bf010ab1b9534cd48047a057efa06a","tid":270811,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:32:54.000Z","msg":"12個球場又係12萬。 6個係11萬"},{"pid":"10e032c2fbbf391ee55c5eed4c43da1ea557271c","tid":270811,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34a356c461738b06586bb2456a61f728bb8f328","tid":270811,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}